<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="687040000t" end="712060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">当这名男婴出生后…</p>
<p begin="720820000t" end="741670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">必须像每个斯巴达人接受检验</p>
<p begin="759610000t" end="805910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">如果他太瘦小、太孱弱<br />生病或是残废</p>
<p begin="807570000t" end="830930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">就会被弃而不顾</p>
<p begin="902250000t" end="959390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">当他长大能够站立后<br />将接受战斗训练的洗礼</p>
<p begin="1179610000t" end="1216320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">被教导绝不退缩、绝不投降</p>
<p begin="1217980000t" end="1266780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">以及为了扞卫斯巴达战死沙场</p>
<p begin="1268870000t" end="1301820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">这是一名勇士一生最大的荣耀</p>
<p begin="1453220000t" end="1498680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">一名七岁的男孩，按照斯巴达惯例</p>
<p begin="1500350000t" end="1552070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">必须离开母亲的怀抱<br />进入弱肉强食的暴力世界</p>
<p begin="1559990000t" end="1605450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">承袭斯巴达战士300年的传统</p>
<p begin="1616300000t" end="1658840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">训练出世上最勇猛的战士</p>
<p begin="1660930000t" end="1706810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">这种被称为教养的训练<br />要强迫男孩战斗</p>
<p begin="1708470000t" end="1744760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">逼他们饿肚子、偷食物</p>
<p begin="1746430000t" end="1790220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">有必要的话，让他们学会杀人</p>
<p begin="1800650000t" end="1830680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">男孩经常受到棒打的惩罚</p>
<p begin="1832350000t" end="1865710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">教导他们忍耐疼痛、绝不手软</p>
<p begin="1882400000t" end="1917430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">他们不断被试炼，被丢到荒野</p>
<p begin="1919100000t" end="1972490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">运用脑力和意志力对抗各种危险</p>
<p begin="1975820000t" end="1997930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">这就是他的成年礼</p>
<p begin="1999600000t" end="2025460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">要在荒野求生</p>
<p begin="2027130000t" end="2072170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">他必须成为强悍的战士<br />才能返回斯巴达</p>
<p begin="2073840000t" end="2095110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">否则就永远回不来</p>
<p begin="2318250000t" end="2347030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">野狼开始绕着男孩兜圈子</p>
<p begin="2348700000t" end="2373300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">钢铁般的利爪</p>
<p begin="2374970000t" end="2397500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">如黑夜般的毛皮</p>
<p begin="2402500000t" end="2415850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">赤红的双眼闪烁</p>
<p begin="2417520000t" end="2456720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">就像来自地狱的宝石</p>
<p begin="2544310000t" end="2584350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">巨大的野狼贪婪地嗅着</p>
<p begin="2585600000t" end="2616460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">准备品尝即将到手的大餐</p>
<p begin="2857960000t" end="2873800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">他并不感到恐惧</p>
<p begin="2879230000t" end="2910920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">反而让他的感官知觉更为敏锐</p>
<p begin="2914260000t" end="2948050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">他的肺部吸入冷空气</p>
<p begin="2953470000t" end="2986830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">被寒风吹动的松树在黑夜摇曳</p>
<p begin="3066910000t" end="3091100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">他的双手稳定</p>
<p begin="3092770000t" end="3115300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">动作敏捷…</p>
<p begin="3116960000t" end="3138240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">完美无缺</p>
<p begin="3395990000t" end="3423520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">这个大家以为必死无疑的男孩</p>
<p begin="3425190000t" end="3473150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">返回他的人民身边<br />成为神圣斯巴达的国王</p>
<p begin="3476910000t" end="3508190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">吾王，雷奥尼达！</p>
<p begin="3573250000t" end="3610790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">他在寒冬中面对野狼的30年后</p>
<p begin="3624970000t" end="3667930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">即将受到另一只巨兽的侵袭</p>
<p begin="3669600000t" end="3719230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">它同样坚忍自信，准备大啖猎物</p>
<p begin="3725490000t" end="3758440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">但这只巨兽包括士兵和战马</p>
<p begin="3760110000t" end="3788050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">利刃和长矛</p>
<p begin="3790140000t" end="3840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">一支由奴隶组成的庞大军队<br />准备吞噬渺小的希腊</p>
<p begin="3841440000t" end="3891070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">消灭世上理智和正义的希望</p>
<p begin="3918180000t" end="3946130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">这只巨兽之所以逼近</p>
<p begin="3973650000t" end="4029130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">是因为雷奥尼达国王激怒了它</p>
<p begin="4735250000t" end="4753600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">很好</p>
<p begin="4756940000t" end="4805730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">再来一次，你在练习场流汗<br />就不会在战场上流血</p>
<p begin="4817830000t" end="4842440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">我父亲告诉我</p>
<p begin="4844110000t" end="4869550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">每个人都有恐惧</p>
<p begin="4870380000t" end="4885810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">但是勇敢面对它</p>
<p begin="4889570000t" end="4900830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">才会变得坚强</p>
<p begin="4902500000t" end="4916260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">王后</p>
<p begin="4917930000t" end="4946290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">波斯使者等着见雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="4971730000t" end="4985500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">事实是</p>
<p begin="4987170000t" end="5023030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">斯巴达战士真正的力量<br />来自他身边的同袍弟兄</p>
<p begin="5030540000t" end="5075590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">只要你给他尊敬和荣耀<br />就会得到他的尊敬和荣耀</p>
<p begin="5081010000t" end="5096020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">首先</p>
<p begin="5103950000t" end="5133970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">-你必须用智力打仗<br />-然后再用决心战斗</p>
<p begin="5156500000t" end="5168180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">什么事？</p>
<p begin="5175690000t" end="5195290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">一名波斯使者在等你</p>
<p begin="5217400000t" end="5233240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">不要忘记今天你学到的</p>
<p begin="5234070000t" end="5261610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">-尊敬和荣耀<br />-尊敬和荣耀</p>
<p begin="5415930000t" end="5460970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">谢隆议员，你抢先和使者谈话</p>
<p begin="5471400000t" end="5495590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">吾王、王后，我只是代为接待贵宾</p>
<p begin="5502680000t" end="5515190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">我猜是吧</p>
<p begin="5527710000t" end="5546060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">波斯人，你在开口之前</p>
<p begin="5547730000t" end="5580260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">要知道斯巴达人，就连国王的使者</p>
<p begin="5581930000t" end="5607790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">都必须为自己说的话负责</p>
<p begin="5617800000t" end="5645320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">现在，告诉我…你带来什么讯息？</p>
<p begin="5656170000t" end="5681190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">泥土和清水</p>
<p begin="5703710000t" end="5740000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">你大老远跑来要泥土和清水？</p>
<p begin="5755850000t" end="5795470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">别想搞鬼或是装笨，波斯人<br />这一招在斯巴达行不通</p>
<p begin="5799640000t" end="5824670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">女人怎么能在男人面前说话？</p>
<p begin="5826340000t" end="5854700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">只有斯巴达女人能生出真正的男人</p>
<p begin="5869710000t" end="5905580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">让我们冷静地边走边谈吧</p>
<p begin="5931440000t" end="5963140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">如果你不想死，也不想被消灭</p>
<p begin="5964810000t" end="5981490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">最好仔细听好，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="5983160000t" end="6030290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">波斯王瑟西斯能征服他要的土地</p>
<p begin="6031960000t" end="6063240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">他率领的军队庞大无比<br />当它前进时土地都会被撼动</p>
<p begin="6064910000t" end="6091600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">而且能把一整条河喝光</p>
<p begin="6093270000t" end="6123300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">神王瑟西斯只有一个要求</p>
<p begin="6126640000t" end="6159170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">向他贡奉泥土和清水</p>
<p begin="6160840000t" end="6202550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">象征斯巴达向波斯王瑟西斯臣服</p>
<p begin="6313070000t" end="6327670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">臣服？</p>
<p begin="6356450000t" end="6375640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">这就有点困难</p>
<p begin="6380220000t" end="6392320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">有听说…</p>
<p begin="6393990000t" end="6420260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">就连雅典人也拒绝臣服</p>
<p begin="6429440000t" end="6481990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">如果那些哲学家和同性恋<br />都有勇气反抗，那么…</p>
<p begin="6483660000t" end="6525790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">-我们必须使用外交手段<br />-当然，斯巴达人…</p>
<p begin="6536210000t" end="6557070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">必须维护斯巴达的名声</p>
<p begin="6558740000t" end="6598780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你最好小心选择你的下一句话</p>
<p begin="6601280000t" end="6627550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">也许那会是你身为国王的<br />最后一句话</p>
<p begin="7032540000t" end="7065490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">“泥土和清水”</p>
<p begin="7118040000t" end="7139320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">疯子！你是个疯子！</p>
<p begin="7140980000t" end="7158080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">泥土和清水</p>
<p begin="7161000000t" end="7183940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">你在下面会找到很多</p>
<p begin="7184780000t" end="7219810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">不论波斯人或希腊人<br />都不杀来使</p>
<p begin="7224400000t" end="7274450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">你戴着被征服的王冠和头颅前来</p>
<p begin="7276120000t" end="7296560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">羞辱我的王后</p>
<p begin="7298220000t" end="7335760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">以奴役和死亡威胁我的人民</p>
<p begin="7337430000t" end="7366630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">我非常小心选择这句话，波斯人</p>
<p begin="7368290000t" end="7387900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">也许你应该跟我一样</p>
<p begin="7389570000t" end="7426270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">这太过分了，你疯了</p>
<p begin="7600190000t" end="7616460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">我疯了？</p>
<p begin="7627300000t" end="7649410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">这就是斯巴达！</p>
<p begin="8514020000t" end="8537380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">欢迎，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="8543640000t" end="8575330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">我们一直在等着你</p>
<p begin="8639980000t" end="8693370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">监事是古代神明的祭师</p>
<p begin="8697540000t" end="8720900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">畸形的变态狂</p>
<p begin="8722560000t" end="8750090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">他们是怪物，不是人类</p>
<p begin="8754260000t" end="8808900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">但是就连雷奥尼达都要贿赂他们</p>
<p begin="8817660000t" end="8866040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">斯巴达王出战<br />必须得到他们的同意</p>
<p begin="8882720000t" end="8923180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">波斯人声称拥有数百万大军</p>
<p begin="8929440000t" end="8962390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">我希望他们是夸大其词</p>
<p begin="8966970000t" end="9009520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">但我们面对的是最庞大的军队</p>
<p begin="9011600000t" end="9044970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">你在说出战略之前</p>
<p begin="9046640000t" end="9069580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">你要奉献什么？</p>
<p begin="9164670000t" end="9208050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">我们要用优越的战斗能力</p>
<p begin="9209720000t" end="9250590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">以及希腊的独特地形歼灭敌军</p>
<p begin="9252260000t" end="9280620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">先向北前进到海岸，然后再…</p>
<p begin="9282290000t" end="9331510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">现在是八月，雷奥尼达<br />而且即将满月</p>
<p begin="9334840000t" end="9366960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">古老的圣典也快要举行了</p>
<p begin="9368630000t" end="9409920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">斯巴达不能在喀尼雅节出战</p>
<p begin="9411170000t" end="9427430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">斯巴达将被烧为平地！</p>
<p begin="9431610000t" end="9447040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">男人将死于沙场</p>
<p begin="9448710000t" end="9485410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">女人和小孩将沦为奴隶</p>
<p begin="9506680000t" end="9557560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">现在，我们要重建福西昂墙</p>
<p begin="9560480000t" end="9583420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">抵挡来自海岸的波斯军队</p>
<p begin="9585090000t" end="9632220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">再把他们诱入称为温泉关的隘口</p>
<p begin="9633890000t" end="9677680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">庞大的敌军在狭窄隘口占劣势</p>
<p begin="9679350000t" end="9705210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">波斯军队一波一波的攻击</p>
<p begin="9706880000t" end="9746500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">将会被斯巴达的壮士击垮</p>
<p begin="9751930000t" end="9795300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">瑟西斯的军队将伤亡惨重<br />他的士兵士气会低落</p>
<p begin="9796970000t" end="9840760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">他将没有选择，只能放弃攻击</p>
<p begin="9842430000t" end="9869540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我们必须求问先知</p>
<p begin="9876630000t" end="9902490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">相信神明，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="9904160000t" end="9937530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">我宁可你们相信自己的判断</p>
<p begin="9939200000t" end="9959630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">你对神明的亵渎</p>
<p begin="9961300000t" end="10005100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">已经惹够多麻烦了</p>
<p begin="10012190000t" end="10042630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">不要再胡言乱语</p>
<p begin="10063490000t" end="10111450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我们将求问先知</p>
<p begin="10132720000t" end="10157750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">畸形的怪胎</p>
<p begin="10167760000t" end="10214050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">是斯巴达脱离黑暗时期时<br />所留下的遗毒</p>
<p begin="10217390000t" end="10250330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">毫无道理可言的传统</p>
<p begin="10252010000t" end="10295800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">就连雷奥尼达<br />也不能违背传统</p>
<p begin="10297460000t" end="10341260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">他必须听从监事的旨令</p>
<p begin="10342920000t" end="10355440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">这就是律法</p>
<p begin="10392570000t" end="10435940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">每一位斯巴达人<br />不管是君民、男女</p>
<p begin="10437610000t" end="10478070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">国王或奴隶<br />都必须遵循律法</p>
<p begin="10826750000t" end="10869710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">监事挑选最美丽的斯巴达少女</p>
<p begin="10871380000t" end="10896400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">成为先知和他们住在一起</p>
<p begin="10898070000t" end="10930600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">她们的美貌也是她们的诅咒</p>
<p begin="10932270000t" end="10970230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">不过这些老怪物<br />有正常男人的欲念</p>
<p begin="10980240000t" end="11021530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">还有地狱般邪恶的心肠</p>
<p begin="11051140000t" end="11083260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">“这是风神的预言</p>
<p begin="11108280000t" end="11129970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">斯巴达将毁灭</p>
<p begin="11159580000t" end="11196700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">全希腊也将瓦解</p>
<p begin="11218390000t" end="11254680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">不能相信凡人</p>
<p begin="11275110000t" end="11307650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">只能听从神明的旨令</p>
<p begin="11345180000t" end="11381890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">要庆祝喀尼雅节”</p>
<p begin="11399820000t" end="11435690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">国王艰辛地爬下峻岭</p>
<p begin="11437360000t" end="11466560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">那些变态的自大狂</p>
<p begin="11468220000t" end="11500340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">无能、病态、昏庸</p>
<p begin="11502010000t" end="11522440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">腐败</p>
<p begin="11556230000t" end="11592510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">你们确实博得波斯神王的欢心</p>
<p begin="11598350000t" end="11619210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">睿智的圣者</p>
<p begin="11622130000t" end="11636730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">没错</p>
<p begin="11638390000t" end="11688030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">当斯巴达燃烧时<br />你们将有用不尽的黄金</p>
<p begin="11689690000t" end="11715550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">会送来最美的处女</p>
<p begin="11720560000t" end="11734320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">每天…</p>
<p begin="11735990000t" end="11773950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">来自波斯帝国每个角落</p>
<p begin="12130970000t" end="12166420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">你的嘴唇可以亲吻你碰触的地方</p>
<p begin="12197700000t" end="12223140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">还是先知让你失去欲望了？</p>
<p begin="12237740000t" end="12268190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">一个被灌醉的少女所说的话</p>
<p begin="12269860000t" end="12286960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">无法剥夺我对你的欲望</p>
<p begin="12328670000t" end="12344100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">那你为何如此冷漠？</p>
<p begin="12374550000t" end="12394570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">因为她虽然只是…</p>
<p begin="12396230000t" end="12455880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">一群色老头的性奴隶</p>
<p begin="12459210000t" end="12491330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">先知的话还是足以<br />摧毁我所热爱的一切</p>
<p begin="12493000000t" end="12529700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">所以你才会辗转难眠<br />离开温暖的被窝？</p>
<p begin="12559730000t" end="12603110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">只有一个女人的话能影响你的心情</p>
<p begin="12611450000t" end="12626880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">那就是我的话</p>
<p begin="12668590000t" end="12693610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">一个国王要如何拯救王国</p>
<p begin="12694450000t" end="12738660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">当他发誓扞卫的律法<br />不准他出战？</p>
<p begin="12768270000t" end="12801640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">问题不是一个斯巴达人、丈夫</p>
<p begin="12803310000t" end="12831670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">或是一个国王该怎么做</p>
<p begin="12838340000t" end="12865040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">你要扪心自问，我的挚爱</p>
<p begin="12881720000t" end="12901740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">一个自由的人该怎么做？</p>
<p begin="13556140000t" end="13597850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">-全部都到齐了吗？<br />-依照您命令的，300壮士</p>
<p begin="13607860000t" end="13640810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">他们都有儿子传宗接代</p>
<p begin="13748420000t" end="13761760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">吾王，我们与你共战</p>
<p begin="13765520000t" end="13786790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">为了斯巴达和自由</p>
<p begin="13788460000t" end="13808060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">誓死奋战！</p>
<p begin="13916090000t" end="13932770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">他是你的儿子</p>
<p begin="13941110000t" end="13969890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">他还年轻，没碰过女人</p>
<p begin="13971560000t" end="14011180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">我还有另外一个儿子可以替代<br />艾斯提诺和其他壮士一样勇猛</p>
<p begin="14014520000t" end="14054970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">我们第一次并肩作战时和他一样大</p>
<p begin="14092930000t" end="14114200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">你是一位好朋友</p>
<p begin="14115870000t" end="14150900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">更是一名最优秀的队长</p>
<p begin="14205960000t" end="14225140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">吾王</p>
<p begin="14234740000t" end="14268100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">吾王，先知下达旨令</p>
<p begin="14269770000t" end="14298130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">监事也说过，不准出战</p>
<p begin="14299800000t" end="14318150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">这是律法，吾王</p>
<p begin="14319820000t" end="14359860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">-斯巴达军队不能出战<br />-他们也不会出战</p>
<p begin="14368620000t" end="14384890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我并没有下达命令</p>
<p begin="14388220000t" end="14423680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">我只是出来散散步、伸伸腿</p>
<p begin="14426180000t" end="14477900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">这300名壮士是我的贴身护卫</p>
<p begin="14480400000t" end="14502090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">军队会留在斯巴达</p>
<p begin="14508340000t" end="14521690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">你要去哪里？</p>
<p begin="14551300000t" end="14573410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">我还没真正想过，不过…</p>
<p begin="14581750000t" end="14603440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">既然你问了</p>
<p begin="14605110000t" end="14632220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">我猜我会向北前进</p>
<p begin="14646820000t" end="14657660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">温泉关？</p>
<p begin="14683940000t" end="14708130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">出发！</p>
<p begin="14710210000t" end="14730650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">出发！</p>
<p begin="14741910000t" end="14752750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">我们该怎么办？</p>
<p begin="14773610000t" end="14786960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">我们能怎么办？</p>
<p begin="14793630000t" end="14811150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">你们拿我没办法</p>
<p begin="14841590000t" end="14879970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">只能留在斯巴达养育后代</p>
<p begin="15357530000t" end="15369620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">吾王！</p>
<p begin="15467640000t" end="15480150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">是的，夫人</p>
<p begin="15641140000t" end="15664080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">带着你的盾牌回来</p>
<p begin="15673260000t" end="15688270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">或是在盾牌上被抬回来</p>
<p begin="15702450000t" end="15716220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">是的，夫人</p>
<p begin="15801300000t" end="15824240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">“再见了，吾爱”</p>
<p begin="15830500000t" end="15852600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">他并没有说出口</p>
<p begin="15857610000t" end="15879710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">他不能眷恋温柔乡</p>
<p begin="15881380000t" end="15901400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">斯巴达壮士不能心软</p>
<p begin="15903070000t" end="15931020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">也不能展现软弱的一面</p>
<p begin="15966050000t" end="16008180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">斯巴达壮士必须强悍勇敢</p>
<p begin="16016520000t" end="16061560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">只能强悍，只能勇敢</p>
<p begin="16346010000t" end="16364780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">我们向前迈进</p>
<p begin="16371870000t" end="16426930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">为了我们的土地和家人<br />也为了我们的自由</p>
<p begin="16434430000t" end="16456120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">我们勇往直前</p>
<p begin="16473640000t" end="16490320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">戴索斯</p>
<p begin="16491990000t" end="16525780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">-这真是个惊喜<br />-今天早上充满惊喜</p>
<p begin="16527440000t" end="16553720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">-我们被耍了<br />-他们只有几百人</p>
<p begin="16554550000t" end="16576240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">-真没想到<br />-闭嘴</p>
<p begin="16580000000t" end="16599600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">这就是他们的军队？</p>
<p begin="16601270000t" end="16642980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">我们一听说斯巴达要出战<br />就急着要加入战争</p>
<p begin="16649650000t" end="16690520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">你们想杀敌的话…欢迎加入我们</p>
<p begin="16693860000t" end="16726390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">你就带这么少士兵对抗敌军？</p>
<p begin="16728060000t" end="16764760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">我以为你的士兵至少和我的一样多</p>
<p begin="16775610000t" end="16793960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">不是吗？</p>
<p begin="16808560000t" end="16825660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">你…</p>
<p begin="16830250000t" end="16842340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">你的职业是什么？</p>
<p begin="16847350000t" end="16869040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">我是陶匠，大王</p>
<p begin="16880710000t" end="16918250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">你，阿卡迪人<br />你是什么职业？</p>
<p begin="16922010000t" end="16956210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">-我是雕塑家<br />-雕塑家</p>
<p begin="16959540000t" end="16979980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">-你呢？<br />-铁匠</p>
<p begin="17025860000t" end="17059230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">斯巴达壮士，你们的职业是什么？</p>
<p begin="17130960000t" end="17150150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">瞧，老友</p>
<p begin="17151820000t" end="17181010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">我的士兵比你的多</p>
<p begin="17280280000t" end="17298210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">今晚不睡觉</p>
<p begin="17309060000t" end="17333670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">国王睡不着</p>
<p begin="17335330000t" end="17357860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">他四十年的生命</p>
<p begin="17359530000t" end="17394980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">等待的就是这光荣的一刻</p>
<p begin="17396650000t" end="17424590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">这一场使用长矛与盾牌</p>
<p begin="17426260000t" end="17462130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">以及利刃刺杀敌军的惨烈战争</p>
<p begin="17479230000t" end="17497160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">他唯一的遗憾</p>
<p begin="17498830000t" end="17536370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">就是他只有300壮士可以牺牲</p>
<p begin="17749080000t" end="17769100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我们被跟踪了</p>
<p begin="17819570000t" end="17841670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">他从斯巴达跟踪到这里</p>
<p begin="17890890000t" end="17920920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">吾王，你看</p>
<p begin="18130300000t" end="18145310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">这里发生了什么事？</p>
<p begin="18150730000t" end="18164080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">村民呢？</p>
<p begin="18175340000t" end="18187020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">波斯人</p>
<p begin="18193690000t" end="18212040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">我猜有20名敌军</p>
<p begin="18235400000t" end="18249160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">那只是前哨部队</p>
<p begin="18282950000t" end="18297960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">但是这些足迹…</p>
<p begin="18411830000t" end="18421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">小心后面！</p>
<p begin="18566980000t" end="18579910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">一个小孩子</p>
<p begin="18908990000t" end="18936100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">屠杀终于停止了</p>
<p begin="18941110000t" end="18959040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">他们…</p>
<p begin="18962790000t" end="19002830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">他们带着来自幽冥的怪物</p>
<p begin="19018680000t" end="19065400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">用他们的利爪和尖牙<br />抓住村民</p>
<p begin="19074570000t" end="19096260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">没有人逃得掉</p>
<p begin="19106270000t" end="19126710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">只有我</p>
<p begin="19249330000t" end="19259760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">村民…</p>
<p begin="19270180000t" end="19289790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">我找到他们了</p>
<p begin="19404900000t" end="19432850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">天理在哪里？</p>
<p begin="19444530000t" end="19464960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">我们死定了</p>
<p begin="19466630000t" end="19485820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">你给我闭嘴</p>
<p begin="19526690000t" end="19579240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">那孩子提到的波斯幽冥怪物<br />故事来自古老的传说</p>
<p begin="19588000000t" end="19615110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">他们专门猎杀人类的灵魂</p>
<p begin="19625120000t" end="19651820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">杀不死也打不败他们</p>
<p begin="19657650000t" end="19699360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">他们是来自幽冥的幽灵战士</p>
<p begin="19721050000t" end="19743160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">幽灵战士？</p>
<p begin="19746080000t" end="19769850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">我们就让他们变成真正的幽灵</p>
<p begin="19997160000t" end="20025110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">我们向温泉关前进</p>
<p begin="20026770000t" end="20059720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">我们向狭窄隘口前进</p>
<p begin="20060560000t" end="20084750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">敌军在那里无用武之力</p>
<p begin="20095590000t" end="20135220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">斯巴达壮士<br />平民士兵、自由奴隶</p>
<p begin="20136880000t" end="20155650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">以及英勇的希腊人</p>
<p begin="20165660000t" end="20196940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">我们这些兄弟、父子</p>
<p begin="20198610000t" end="20218630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">勇往直前</p>
<p begin="20225310000t" end="20267430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">为了尊严、为了职责<br />为了荣耀勇往直前</p>
<p begin="20269100000t" end="20299960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">你们看，波斯舰队</p>
<p begin="20351260000t" end="20388800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">我们向地狱之口前进</p>
<p begin="20479300000t" end="20499750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">让我们看着这些狗杂种</p>
<p begin="20502250000t" end="20542710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">被愤怒的希腊天神吞噬<br />来吧！</p>
<p begin="20571060000t" end="20582750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">没错</p>
<p begin="20629880000t" end="20654480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">看起来的确会下雨</p>
<p begin="20687850000t" end="20719970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">宙斯掷起闪电刺向天空</p>
<p begin="20722890000t" end="20763340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">掀起狂风大浪翻覆波斯战舰</p>
<p begin="20774590000t" end="20793790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">太好了</p>
<p begin="20921820000t" end="20950610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">我们当中只有一人保持冷静</p>
<p begin="21009840000t" end="21029440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">只有他</p>
<p begin="21031110000t" end="21049460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">我们的国王</p>
<p begin="21230060000t" end="21249240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">王后？</p>
<p begin="21300960000t" end="21314310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">王后…</p>
<p begin="21315980000t" end="21349340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">在庭院与已婚妇女谈话<br />才能避嫌</p>
<p begin="21351010000t" end="21367700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">恐怕我所担心的</p>
<p begin="21369360000t" end="21394810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">不是闲话和礼仪，议员</p>
<p begin="21411490000t" end="21429840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">有必要这么小心吗？</p>
<p begin="21431510000t" end="21458200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">我不得不小心隔墙有耳</p>
<p begin="21459870000t" end="21496990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">谢隆在这里布满眼线<br />让斯巴达人心中充满怀疑恐惧</p>
<p begin="21501160000t" end="21535360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">你似乎认为斯巴达人都在对付你</p>
<p begin="21541620000t" end="21562060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">我希望他们只是对付我</p>
<p begin="21588750000t" end="21623790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">许多议员都愿意投票</p>
<p begin="21625450000t" end="21643810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">同意出兵支援雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="21647140000t" end="21667160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">但是你要给他们好处</p>
<p begin="21689680000t" end="21710960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">你能安排我在议会发言吗？</p>
<p begin="21716380000t" end="21740570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">他们想听真理，我会告诉他们</p>
<p begin="21742240000t" end="21763930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">什么真理？王后</p>
<p begin="21767260000t" end="21787280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">自由必须努力争取而来</p>
<p begin="21788950000t" end="21822320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">并且要付出鲜血的代价</p>
<p begin="21845260000t" end="21871530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">我会尽力召集议会</p>
<p begin="21875700000t" end="21914080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">让你在议会厅向他们发言</p>
<p begin="21917410000t" end="21935760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">-我欠你一份人情<br />-不</p>
<p begin="21939100000t" end="21980810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">雷奥尼达不只是你的国王<br />也是我的</p>
<p begin="22228970000t" end="22247740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">我明明看到战舰撞上礁石</p>
<p begin="22258590000t" end="22272350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">怎么会这样？</p>
<p begin="22273180000t" end="22306970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">你看到的只是波斯军队的一小部分</p>
<p begin="22313640000t" end="22337830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">我们不可能打赢他们</p>
<p begin="22377040000t" end="22388720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">你为什么在笑？</p>
<p begin="22411240000t" end="22430420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">阿卡迪人</p>
<p begin="22432090000t" end="22462540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">我身经百战</p>
<p begin="22465040000t" end="22491740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">从来没遇到一支敌军能让我们</p>
<p begin="22493400000t" end="22515090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">英勇地战死</p>
<p begin="22523020000t" end="22540530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">我只希望</p>
<p begin="22541370000t" end="22569730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">来自全世界<br />对付我们的军队之中</p>
<p begin="22570560000t" end="22607270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">或许波斯军队能够让我英勇地战死</p>
<p begin="22721550000t" end="22744910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">快走！</p>
<p begin="22758250000t" end="22777440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">给我快走，狗杂种</p>
<p begin="22864190000t" end="22875450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">快点！</p>
<p begin="22898810000t" end="22914240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">我命令你们前进！</p>
<p begin="22948030000t" end="22963870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">停下来！</p>
<p begin="22972220000t" end="22985150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">谁是指挥官？</p>
<p begin="23016010000t" end="23042700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">我是</p>
<p begin="23044370000t" end="23066890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">全世界的统治者</p>
<p begin="23075240000t" end="23114020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">众神之神、万王之王的使者</p>
<p begin="23115690000t" end="23131960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">我奉吾王之命</p>
<p begin="23133630000t" end="23171160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">要求见你们的指挥官</p>
<p begin="23208700000t" end="23267930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">给我听好<br />你们以为杀死十几个人就能吓唬我们？</p>
<p begin="23269600000t" end="23304630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">这里到处都有我们的哨兵</p>
<p begin="23306300000t" end="23353430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">你们这道小小的围墙<br />只要受到波斯大军的攻击</p>
<p begin="23355100000t" end="23418080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">就会像秋风扫落叶一样被吹到地上</p>
<p begin="23535280000t" end="23558220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">我们的祖先建筑这道围墙</p>
<p begin="23565730000t" end="23604930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">用的是希腊土地底下的古老石头</p>
<p begin="23609100000t" end="23632880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">我们这些斯巴达壮士</p>
<p begin="23635800000t" end="23660820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">则是用你们的波斯哨兵当泥浆</p>
<p begin="23666660000t" end="23706280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">你们会为这种野蛮行为付出代价</p>
<p begin="23897720000t" end="23913570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">我的手臂！</p>
<p begin="23939430000t" end="23957780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">已经不是你的了</p>
<p begin="23960700000t" end="24007000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">快滚吧<br />告诉瑟西斯我们是自由斗士</p>
<p begin="24010750000t" end="24024520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">不是奴隶</p>
<p begin="24026190000t" end="24038280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">你再不走的话</p>
<p begin="24039950000t" end="24070810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">我们就要把你也当成泥浆</p>
<p begin="24074980000t" end="24091250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">你错了</p>
<p begin="24092920000t" end="24117110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">你们不会是奴隶</p>
<p begin="24135040000t" end="24169660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">你们的女人会是奴隶</p>
<p begin="24173000000t" end="24226390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">你们的子女<br />和老人也会是奴隶</p>
<p begin="24228050000t" end="24255580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">但是你们不会是奴隶</p>
<p begin="24257250000t" end="24298120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">到了今天中午<br />你们都会是死人</p>
<p begin="24309800000t" end="24369860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">波斯帝国的千军万马即将降临</p>
<p begin="24373620000t" end="24408650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">太阳会被我们的千万支乱箭遮蔽</p>
<p begin="24426590000t" end="24453280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">那我们就在阴影下奋勇作战</p>
<p begin="24468710000t" end="24486650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">围墙很坚固</p>
<p begin="24488310000t" end="24520430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">绝对能把敌军逼进温泉关</p>
<p begin="24523350000t" end="24550040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">弟兄发现山上有路通到后方吗？</p>
<p begin="24555050000t" end="24575480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">没有，王上</p>
<p begin="24578400000t" end="24594670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">有一条小路，吾王</p>
<p begin="24599260000t" end="24616780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">就在西边山脊的另一边</p>
<p begin="24623450000t" end="24640130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">一条古老的羊肠小径</p>
<p begin="24641800000t" end="24670160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">波斯军队能从那里突袭我们</p>
<p begin="24671830000t" end="24709370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">别再往前踏一步，怪物</p>
<p begin="24725630000t" end="24761920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">吾王，我谦卑地请你听我一言</p>
<p begin="24763590000t" end="24796960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">-小心我一剑把你刺死<br />-我不准你这么做</p>
<p begin="24902060000t" end="24914570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">请原谅队长</p>
<p begin="24921250000t" end="24936260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">他是位优秀的军人</p>
<p begin="24942100000t" end="24968380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">不过不是很有礼貌</p>
<p begin="24970050000t" end="25010500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">不需要原谅，勇敢的国王<br />我知道我长得很畸形</p>
<p begin="25015090000t" end="25035530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">你披着斯巴达军人的红披风</p>
<p begin="25041370000t" end="25097670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">我是厄菲阿尔特，斯巴达之子</p>
<p begin="25103930000t" end="25144390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">我母亲引诱我父亲逃离斯巴达</p>
<p begin="25146050000t" end="25160650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">把我丢下来等死</p>
<p begin="25166070000t" end="25194020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">你的盾牌和盔甲？</p>
<p begin="25203190000t" end="25214460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">是我父亲的</p>
<p begin="25233220000t" end="25274100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">英勇的国王，我求你让我</p>
<p begin="25275770000t" end="25325820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">为你效命沙场，恢复父亲的名誉</p>
<p begin="25329150000t" end="25387550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">我父亲教我不能心存恐惧<br />以及如何让长矛、盾牌和剑</p>
<p begin="25389210000t" end="25416740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">像我的心一样<br />成为我身体的一部分</p>
<p begin="25420910000t" end="25454280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">我会和你并肩作战</p>
<p begin="25455950000t" end="25477640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">洗刷我父亲的污名</p>
<p begin="25529350000t" end="25550210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">你的技术不错</p>
<p begin="25551880000t" end="25567730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">我能杀死很多波斯军人</p>
<p begin="25626530000t" end="25637380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">把盾牌抬高</p>
<p begin="25644470000t" end="25671160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">-国王？<br />-把盾牌尽量抬高</p>
<p begin="25753330000t" end="25783770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">你父亲应该教你方阵的战术</p>
<p begin="25790450000t" end="25803380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">方阵能抵挡</p>
<p begin="25808800000t" end="25838000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">任何攻击</p>
<p begin="25839660000t" end="25868860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">这是我们最有利的武器</p>
<p begin="25877200000t" end="25913490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">每名士兵用盾牌保护左方的同袍</p>
<p begin="25915160000t" end="25947270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">从大腿到颈部的安全</p>
<p begin="25948940000t" end="25995650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">出现任何一个缺口，方阵就会瓦解</p>
<p begin="26009830000t" end="26041950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">从大腿到颈部，厄菲阿尔特</p>
<p begin="26062390000t" end="26086580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">抱歉</p>
<p begin="26088250000t" end="26114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">-不是每个人都能当士兵<br />-可是我…</p>
<p begin="26114940000t" end="26139960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">-你想帮助斯巴达打胜仗<br />-是的</p>
<p begin="26141630000t" end="26193350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">就把死人从战场抬走<br />照顾伤兵，替他们拿水</p>
<p begin="26195020000t" end="26211700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">至于上场打仗…</p>
<p begin="26225050000t" end="26244230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">我不能用你</p>
<p begin="26262590000t" end="26276770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">你…</p>
<p begin="26355600000t" end="26396890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">母亲！父亲！你们错了！</p>
<p begin="26429420000t" end="26446940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">你们错了！</p>
<p begin="26448610000t" end="26494070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">雷奥尼达！你也错了！</p>
<p begin="26498660000t" end="26523680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">派遣福西昂人驻守羊肠小径</p>
<p begin="26525350000t" end="26570390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">祈求没有人告诉波斯人这条羊肠小径</p>
<p begin="26627530000t" end="26637960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">地震</p>
<p begin="26648810000t" end="26660900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">不，队长</p>
<p begin="26677170000t" end="26696350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">是敌军来了</p>
<p begin="26935340000t" end="26967460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">我们在这里抵挡他们</p>
<p begin="26969130000t" end="26991650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">我们要在这里誓死奋战</p>
<p begin="26997490000t" end="27019590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">也要在这里歼灭敌军</p>
<p begin="27022930000t" end="27041700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">证明你们的实力</p>
<p begin="27069230000t" end="27094250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">弟兄们，记得这一天</p>
<p begin="27095920000t" end="27133040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">你们将名留千古</p>
<p begin="27244400000t" end="27261920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">斯巴达人</p>
<p begin="27263590000t" end="27284860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">把武器放下</p>
<p begin="27453780000t" end="27476300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">波斯人</p>
<p begin="27482140000t" end="27502990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">有胆就过来</p>
<p begin="27717790000t" end="27728630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">稳住！</p>
<p begin="27762420000t" end="27778270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">挡住他们</p>
<p begin="27782440000t" end="27818310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">把他们全部歼灭</p>
<p begin="27835410000t" end="27847500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">稳住！</p>
<p begin="27960530000t" end="27975960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">用力推！</p>
<p begin="28014340000t" end="28038530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">你们只有这么点力气吗？</p>
<p begin="28060220000t" end="28080240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">用力推！用力推！</p>
<p begin="28181170000t" end="28191180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">现在！</p>
<p begin="28314640000t" end="28324230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">用力推！</p>
<p begin="28765090000t" end="28790950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">一个都别放过</p>
<p begin="28794280000t" end="28811800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">绝不手软</p>
<p begin="29605090000t" end="29626360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">他们看起来很渴</p>
<p begin="29637210000t" end="29666820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">那就让他们喝海水吧</p>
<p begin="29695600000t" end="29722290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">把他们推向悬崖</p>
<p begin="29958780000t" end="29980470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">停下来！</p>
<p begin="30001320000t" end="30022180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">这是好的开始</p>
<p begin="30248650000t" end="30269090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">举起盾牌！</p>
<p begin="30328310000t" end="30344160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">波斯人是懦夫</p>
<p begin="30421740000t" end="30450940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">-你在笑什么？<br />-谁叫你那么说</p>
<p begin="30459280000t" end="30488470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">-说什么？<br />-“在阴影下作战”</p>
<p begin="30631120000t" end="30650300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">站起来</p>
<p begin="30883040000t" end="30910150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">今天，斯巴达壮士不会死</p>
<p begin="31160810000t" end="31175830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">不必急，战士们</p>
<p begin="31437340000t" end="31457780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">我们运用平时的训练</p>
<p begin="31458610000t" end="31473630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">发挥我们天生</p>
<p begin="31475290000t" end="31505320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">作战的能力</p>
<p begin="31578730000t" end="31608760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">不饶一命、绝不手软</p>
<p begin="31610430000t" end="31625440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">一个好的开始</p>
<p begin="32319890000t" end="32352840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">-我深怕你不会来<br />-抱歉，我儿子…</p>
<p begin="32354510000t" end="32410390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">他跟其他的小孩一样<br />请你不要道歉</p>
<p begin="32420400000t" end="32441680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">令郎明年就会被带去训练</p>
<p begin="32447930000t" end="32487970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">这对一位斯巴达母亲来说很残忍</p>
<p begin="32498820000t" end="32544700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">我是很难过，不过这是必要的</p>
<p begin="32568890000t" end="32611430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">你两天后<br />可以在议会的议员面前发言</p>
<p begin="32629780000t" end="32650220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">我丈夫撑不了两天</p>
<p begin="32654390000t" end="32673990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">好好利用这两天</p>
<p begin="32694850000t" end="32714870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">大家都知道</p>
<p begin="32716530000t" end="32745310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">谢隆一直在觊觎你</p>
<p begin="32746980000t" end="32775340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">你必须先说服他</p>
<p begin="32777010000t" end="32798280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">让他支持你</p>
<p begin="32801200000t" end="32826640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">你就能说服议会</p>
<p begin="32834990000t" end="32852500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">谢谢你</p>
<p begin="32855840000t" end="32880030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">你既睿智又好心</p>
<p begin="33150300000t" end="33168240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">你母亲在这里</p>
<p begin="33232880000t" end="33262080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">如果他想当国王<br />你就得看好他</p>
<p begin="33269590000t" end="33294610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">他和他美丽的母亲…</p>
<p begin="33308790000t" end="33327560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">最好都不要出事</p>
<p begin="33488140000t" end="33503150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">不要！</p>
<p begin="33535690000t" end="33589910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">我们的希腊同伴要求<br />也要一起对抗波斯</p>
<p begin="33592830000t" end="33606170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">很好</p>
<p begin="33607840000t" end="33635790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">有一项任务他们能够胜任</p>
<p begin="33640790000t" end="33657470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">我要你转告戴索斯</p>
<p begin="33659140000t" end="33704600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">请他带20名最好的士兵<br />准备下一场战争</p>
<p begin="33706270000t" end="33724620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499">雷奥尼达王</p>
<p begin="33749650000t" end="33787600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500">-史特里欧，先喘口气<br />-是，吾王</p>
<p begin="33794280000t" end="33815550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501">波斯人接近了</p>
<p begin="33829310000t" end="33867680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502">只有一小群人，不像是要攻击</p>
<p begin="33905220000t" end="33941090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503">-队长，你负责坐镇<br />-可是…</p>
<p begin="33942760000t" end="33954850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504">放心，老朋友</p>
<p begin="33956520000t" end="34002400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505">我若被刺杀，斯巴达就会派出大军</p>
<p begin="34011580000t" end="34037850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506">我祈祷他们有这么愚蠢</p>
<p begin="34048700000t" end="34065800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507">也祈祷…</p>
<p begin="34071220000t" end="34092910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508">我们有这么幸运</p>
<p begin="34124610000t" end="34142120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509">况且</p>
<p begin="34164650000t" end="34198010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510">没理由不能好好商量</p>
<p begin="34201350000t" end="34217200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511">对吧？</p>
<p begin="34230550000t" end="34240560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512">没错，吾王</p>
<p begin="34434500000t" end="34456610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513">让我猜一猜</p>
<p begin="34464110000t" end="34494140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514">你一定是…瑟西斯</p>
<p begin="34614260000t" end="34636370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515">来吧，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="34650550000t" end="34668480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516">让我们一起讲讲道理</p>
<p begin="34670990000t" end="34690590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517">你这么做是浪费生命</p>
<p begin="34694760000t" end="34726880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518">你和300壮士继续顽强抵抗</p>
<p begin="34728540000t" end="34760240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519">就为了一场误会而白白牺牲</p>
<p begin="34766920000t" end="34787350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle520">这简直就是疯狂</p>
<p begin="34793610000t" end="34821970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle521">-我们可以进行文化交流的<br />-难道你没注意到吗？</p>
<p begin="34823640000t" end="34847410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle522">我们早上不都在文化交流？</p>
<p begin="34853670000t" end="34876190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle523">你们是很有趣的部落</p>
<p begin="34877860000t" end="34899550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle524">你就算面对死亡…</p>
<p begin="34901220000t" end="34942510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle525">以及我这天神，还是这么固执</p>
<p begin="34944180000t" end="34964610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle526">想要对抗我<br />不是很聪明的举动，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="34971290000t" end="34993810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle527">我的敌人会死得很惨</p>
<p begin="34995480000t" end="35024260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle528">因为我为了获胜<br />会很乐意牺牲手下</p>
<p begin="35025920000t" end="35052200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle529">而我会为了我的手下牺牲自己</p>
<p begin="35053870000t" end="35096410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle530">你们希腊人擅于运用逻辑<br />我建议你理智一点</p>
<p begin="35098080000t" end="35133950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle531">想一想你拼命要保护的家园</p>
<p begin="35135620000t" end="35160640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle532">我一下令就能把它烧成灰烬</p>
<p begin="35162730000t" end="35177330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle533">你也要想想女人的下场</p>
<p begin="35183580000t" end="35209020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle534">你很显然不了解她们</p>
<p begin="35210690000t" end="35245730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle535">你们这么弱，我派她们来就够了</p>
<p begin="35256990000t" end="35282430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle536">你有很多奴隶，瑟西斯</p>
<p begin="35291610000t" end="35314550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle537">却很少战士</p>
<p begin="35316210000t" end="35355840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle538">他们很快就会害怕我的长矛</p>
<p begin="35359590000t" end="35384200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle539">多于害怕你的鞭子</p>
<p begin="35422570000t" end="35450930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle540">他们怕的不是我的鞭子</p>
<p begin="35478460000t" end="35495140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle541">而是我的神力</p>
<p begin="35502650000t" end="35547700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle542">但是我是一个大方的神<br />可以让你享尽荣华富贵</p>
<p begin="35551870000t" end="35576060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle543">甚至让你成为全希腊之主</p>
<p begin="35582310000t" end="35621100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle544">你可以代表我进军欧罗巴</p>
<p begin="35622770000t" end="35649050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle545">你的雅典对手</p>
<p begin="35651970000t" end="35673650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle546">也会向你跪拜</p>
<p begin="35680750000t" end="35708690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle547">只要你愿意向我跪拜</p>
<p begin="35717030000t" end="35739550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle548">你是很大方</p>
<p begin="35745390000t" end="35769580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle549">也很有神力</p>
<p begin="35776670000t" end="35792940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle550">万王之王</p>
<p begin="35794610000t" end="35833810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle551">傻瓜才会拒绝这么好的条件</p>
<p begin="35839650000t" end="35859670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle552">但是…</p>
<p begin="35868850000t" end="35897210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle553">跪拜这件事…</p>
<p begin="35898880000t" end="35944340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle554">我杀了这么多你的士兵</p>
<p begin="35946010000t" end="35984380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle555">使了太多力，大腿有点抽筋</p>
<p begin="35986050000t" end="36006900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle556">要我跪拜有点困难</p>
<p begin="36009820000t" end="36043190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle557">你们的牺牲不会有任何荣耀</p>
<p begin="36044860000t" end="36081150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle558">我会让斯巴达从历史上消失</p>
<p begin="36082810000t" end="36114930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle559">烧掉每一本希腊史书</p>
<p begin="36116600000t" end="36149960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle560">挖掉每名历史学家的眼睛</p>
<p begin="36151630000t" end="36174150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle561">连他的舌头都会被割掉</p>
<p begin="36175820000t" end="36235880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle562">只要提起斯巴达或是雷奥尼达<br />就会被处以死刑</p>
<p begin="36242140000t" end="36275090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle563">世人不会知道你们存在过</p>
<p begin="36296360000t" end="36342240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle564">世人会知道自由斗士对抗暴君</p>
<p begin="36344320000t" end="36379360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle565">他们勇敢地以寡敌众</p>
<p begin="36383530000t" end="36414810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle566">而且在战役结束前</p>
<p begin="36417310000t" end="36446930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle567">就连神王也会流血</p>
<p begin="36520750000t" end="36542860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle568">你今天打得很好</p>
<p begin="36556200000t" end="36575390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle569">像个女人</p>
<p begin="36587070000t" end="36603750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle570">你也一样</p>
<p begin="36605420000t" end="36636280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle571">我受了伤你才赶得上我</p>
<p begin="36641290000t" end="36690920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle572">我冲得太快<br />你根本看不到我</p>
<p begin="36697180000t" end="36728880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle573">你只会跟老太婆一样慢</p>
<p begin="36738470000t" end="36754730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle574">你这是吃不到葡萄…</p>
<p begin="36756400000t" end="36781430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle575">说葡萄酸</p>
<p begin="36808960000t" end="36832310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle576">快点，大伙儿</p>
<p begin="36853170000t" end="36875690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle577">把这些波斯人堆得更高一些</p>
<p begin="36906970000t" end="36934910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle578">除非我猜错</p>
<p begin="36940750000t" end="36970780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle579">今晚将有一场苦战</p>
<p begin="37209770000t" end="37261490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle580">500年来<br />他们替波斯王干尽坏事</p>
<p begin="37263160000t" end="37286520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle581">眼睛像夜晚一般黑</p>
<p begin="37288180000t" end="37308200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle582">满嘴都是尖牙</p>
<p begin="37329480000t" end="37343240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle583">没有灵魂</p>
<p begin="37426240000t" end="37473790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle584">他们是瑟西斯王的锦衣卫<br />波斯军队的菁英</p>
<p begin="37491720000t" end="37523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle585">全亚洲最致命的战斗部队</p>
<p begin="37530510000t" end="37551360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle586">他们是幽灵战士</p>
<p begin="37633110000t" end="37667310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle587">波斯神王犯了一个致命大错</p>
<p begin="37672320000t" end="37689840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle588">太过于轻敌</p>
<p begin="37712360000t" end="37739890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle589">太容易被激怒、太着急</p>
<p begin="37746560000t" end="37771170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle590">他在我们尚未受伤和疲倦前</p>
<p begin="37772840000t" end="37808290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle591">就派出精英部队攻击我们</p>
<p begin="37813290000t" end="37829980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle592">瑟西斯受诱上钩</p>
<p begin="37831640000t" end="37850000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle593">斯巴达壮士，用力</p>
<p begin="37956770000t" end="37967200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle594">幽灵战士</p>
<p begin="37977210000t" end="38006820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle595">我们让他们成为真正的幽灵</p>
<p begin="38448930000t" end="38457690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle596">父亲！</p>
<p begin="39520000000t" end="39532930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle597">吾王！</p>
<p begin="40260320000t" end="40279920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle598">阿卡迪勇士，上啊！</p>
<p begin="40302860000t" end="40330810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle599">让斯巴达人见识我们的本事</p>
<p begin="40336650000t" end="40350830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle600">快上啊！</p>
<p begin="40445090000t" end="40464270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle601">他们大声叫骂</p>
<p begin="40465940000t" end="40497640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle602">拿剑乱刺<br />简直是一群乌合之众</p>
<p begin="40509320000t" end="40534760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle603">把幽灵战士弄得手忙脚乱</p>
<p begin="40545190000t" end="40572720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle604">勇敢的菜鸟发挥了作用</p>
<p begin="41049020000t" end="41067790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle605">幽灵战士</p>
<p begin="41069450000t" end="41095320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle606">未能达到国王的期望</p>
<p begin="41096990000t" end="41126590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle607">波斯王自以为是神</p>
<p begin="41133690000t" end="41183330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle608">这时却像凡人一样感到一阵寒意</p>
<p begin="41254220000t" end="41275500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle609">向吾王致敬！</p>
<p begin="41279250000t" end="41299270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle610">向死去的弟兄致敬！</p>
<p begin="41300940000t" end="41328890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle611">瑟西斯这下还敢派谁来？</p>
<p begin="41332210000t" end="41359330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle612">什么都阻止不了我们了</p>
<p begin="41368090000t" end="41403550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle613">就连国王心中也存有获胜的希望</p>
<p begin="41405200000t" end="41438580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle614">这很疯狂，但我们心存希望：</p>
<p begin="41442750000t" end="41496970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle615">“能够击败杀不尽的敌军<br />以寡敌众、获得胜利</p>
<p begin="41498640000t" end="41525740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle616">我们能坚守温泉关</p>
<p begin="41527420000t" end="41548690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle617">我们可以打赢”</p>
<p begin="41624600000t" end="41642120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle618">黎明来临</p>
<p begin="41648370000t" end="41688820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle619">传来鞭打声和野蛮人的吼叫声</p>
<p begin="41690500000t" end="41729290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle620">后面的波斯军大喊“前进”</p>
<p begin="41748060000t" end="41786010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle621">前面的波斯军大叫“撤退”</p>
<p begin="41847320000t" end="41872350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle622">我们看到一只可怕的怪兽</p>
<p begin="41874020000t" end="41915310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle623">它来自波斯帝国的黑暗角落</p>
<p begin="42417480000t" end="42432910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle624">波斯士兵打不赢我们</p>
<p begin="42437080000t" end="42463770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle625">就派出奇形怪状的野兽</p>
<p begin="42474200000t" end="42522160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle626">千军万马向我们攻击<br />全亚洲的军队都聚集在这里</p>
<p begin="42523830000t" end="42568460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle627">冲向这条狭窄的隘口<br />庞大的军队也拿我们没辙</p>
<p begin="42912140000t" end="42931740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle628">他们数以百计的被击杀</p>
<p begin="42933410000t" end="42989710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle629">被吓破胆的伤兵爬回敌军阵营</p>
<p begin="43155710000t" end="43197420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle630">瑟西斯王对他的将军很不满</p>
<p begin="43199090000t" end="43224950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle631">于是杀鸡儆猴</p>
<p begin="43393870000t" end="43431820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle632">他又派出来自遥远国度的怪兽</p>
<p begin="43547350000t" end="43568630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle633">但是它们的动作笨拙</p>
<p begin="43570290000t" end="43594070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle634">波斯兵血流成河，使它们打滑</p>
<p begin="43958180000t" end="43982790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle635">-你还没死吗？<br />-总得有人保护你呀</p>
<p begin="43984460000t" end="44000720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle636">现在我有点忙</p>
<p begin="44403210000t" end="44428230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle637">重新组队！</p>
<p begin="44460350000t" end="44471610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle638">艾斯提诺！</p>
<p begin="44478700000t" end="44495800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle639">吾儿！</p>
<p begin="44585060000t" end="44601740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle640">艾斯提诺！</p>
<p begin="44603410000t" end="44630940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle641">不！</p>
<p begin="44863670000t" end="44884940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle642">这是漫长的一天</p>
<p begin="44888280000t" end="44909970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle643">我们失去一些同袍</p>
<p begin="44911630000t" end="44943750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle644">但是每一位<br />都是朋友或是亲人</p>
<p begin="44965850000t" end="45005060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle645">当队长看到自己儿子的头颅被砍掉后</p>
<p begin="45006730000t" end="45025500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle646">他不顾命令往前冲</p>
<p begin="45027170000t" end="45054690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle647">发疯似地砍杀敌军</p>
<p begin="45307450000t" end="45333300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle648">队长失去爱子伤痛得哭号</p>
<p begin="45334140000t" end="45371680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle649">比最沉重的战鼓更让敌人害怕</p>
<p begin="45373340000t" end="45413380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle650">要靠三名弟兄才能把他拖回来</p>
<p begin="45416720000t" end="45440080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle651">那天的胜利属于我们</p>
<p begin="45444250000t" end="45470940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle652">但是我们没有高歌庆功</p>
<p begin="45871760000t" end="45918060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle653">神明很残忍，把你造成这模样</p>
<p begin="45941830000t" end="45983120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle654">斯巴达人把你放逐<br />也很残忍</p>
<p begin="46019820000t" end="46044010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle655">但是我很慈悲</p>
<p begin="46109080000t" end="46130350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle656">你此生想要的一切</p>
<p begin="46142860000t" end="46160380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle657">你欲求的每一种欢愉</p>
<p begin="46182490000t" end="46228370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle658">你被希腊同胞所剥夺的一切</p>
<p begin="46236710000t" end="46259230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle659">我都可以赐给你</p>
<p begin="46271740000t" end="46295930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle660">因为我很慈悲</p>
<p begin="46435240000t" end="46468610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle661">尊崇我是你唯一的国王和神明</p>
<p begin="46479870000t" end="46496970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle662">是的</p>
<p begin="46511570000t" end="46559530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle663">带领我的军队前往羊肠小径<br />从后方突袭斯巴达军队</p>
<p begin="46561200000t" end="46583720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle664">你就会得到你想要的一切</p>
<p begin="46668390000t" end="46700090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle665">是的，我全都要</p>
<p begin="46704260000t" end="46723440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle666">财富</p>
<p begin="46724280000t" end="46740130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle667">女人</p>
<p begin="46760150000t" end="46777250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle668">还有一件事</p>
<p begin="46808950000t" end="46835640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle669">我要一套军服</p>
<p begin="46880680000t" end="46892360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle670">没问题</p>
<p begin="46914050000t" end="46925730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle671">你会发现…</p>
<p begin="46936990000t" end="46956180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle672">我很慈悲</p>
<p begin="46967440000t" end="47009980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle673">我不像雷奥尼达一样<br />要你站起来</p>
<p begin="47030830000t" end="47047930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle674">我只要你…</p>
<p begin="47055440000t" end="47069620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle675">跪下来</p>
<p begin="47346150000t" end="47365750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle676">好美的夜晚</p>
<p begin="47379930000t" end="47419970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle677">是的，但我不是请你来聊天的<br />谢隆</p>
<p begin="47426230000t" end="47447500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle678">这一点你很确定</p>
<p begin="47461260000t" end="47487960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle679">你从来不肯跟我说话</p>
<p begin="47493800000t" end="47526330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle680">你要什么吗？喝一杯吗？</p>
<p begin="47528000000t" end="47546350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle681">那是毒药吗？</p>
<p begin="47550520000t" end="47578880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle682">抱歉让你失望，这只是清水</p>
<p begin="47676060000t" end="47713600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle683">听说你要到议会发言</p>
<p begin="47714430000t" end="47727360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle684">是的</p>
<p begin="47733620000t" end="47766990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle685">请你帮我说服议员派兵支援国王</p>
<p begin="47772830000t" end="47789090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle686">是的</p>
<p begin="47795760000t" end="47821620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle687">我能看到我们俩站在一起</p>
<p begin="47823290000t" end="47866670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle688">我是政客，你是女战士<br />我们都有共识</p>
<p begin="47880020000t" end="47895030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle689">但是我为什么要帮你？</p>
<p begin="47904620000t" end="47944250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle690">这证明你支持国王<br />他正在为我们所喝的清水奋战</p>
<p begin="47947580000t" end="47963430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle691">没错</p>
<p begin="47967190000t" end="47993460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle692">但这是政治，不是战争</p>
<p begin="47996800000t" end="48011810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle693">雷奥尼达是个理想主义者</p>
<p begin="48015980000t" end="48055190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle694">我太了解你这种人<br />为了自己的利益让别人去送死</p>
<p begin="48056860000t" end="48106070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle695">是你的丈夫，我们的国王<br />率领最顶尖的300壮士去送死</p>
<p begin="48107740000t" end="48154040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle696">他违背了律法<br />没征求议会同意就出兵</p>
<p begin="48159040000t" end="48189070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle697">-我只是个务实者<br />-你是个投机分子</p>
<p begin="48198670000t" end="48242040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle698">你和雷奥尼达一样傻<br />世上每一个人都能被收买</p>
<p begin="48243300000t" end="48289170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle699">不是人人都平等<br />这才是斯巴达的律法</p>
<p begin="48325880000t" end="48350070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle700">我很钦佩你的勇气</p>
<p begin="48363420000t" end="48380520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle701">不过你是</p>
<p begin="48385100000t" end="48408460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle702">女人，就算是王后</p>
<p begin="48410130000t" end="48449330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle703">也不能走进议会动摇男人的心</p>
<p begin="48451000000t" end="48475610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle704">掌控议会的是我</p>
<p begin="48477280000t" end="48497720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle705">我能只手遮天</p>
<p begin="48542340000t" end="48577800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle706">我也可以用这只手掐死你</p>
<p begin="48588640000t" end="48625340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle707">你可以去议会，但没人会听你的</p>
<p begin="48627010000t" end="48684570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle708">雷奥尼达不会得到支援的<br />就算他活着回来，若没有我帮忙</p>
<p begin="48686240000t" end="48715850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle709">他也会坐牢或甚至更惨</p>
<p begin="48753390000t" end="48767990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle710">你热爱斯巴达吗？</p>
<p begin="48772990000t" end="48790090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle711">是的</p>
<p begin="48791760000t" end="48814280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle712">-还有你的国王？<br />-我爱他</p>
<p begin="48872670000t" end="48909790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle713">你丈夫为家园和爱妻奋战</p>
<p begin="48916470000t" end="48939410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle714">你能给我什么…</p>
<p begin="48947330000t" end="48976940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle715">好让我帮你说服议会出兵支援？</p>
<p begin="49016570000t" end="49043260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle716">你这务实者要我做什么？</p>
<p begin="49089560000t" end="49106660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle717">你应该很清楚</p>
<p begin="49251390000t" end="49278080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle718">这不会很快结束</p>
<p begin="49288510000t" end="49313530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle719">你也一定不会喜欢</p>
<p begin="49318950000t" end="49341480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle720">因为我不是你的国王</p>
<p begin="49589640000t" end="49607570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle721">狄里欧？</p>
<p begin="49627590000t" end="49668050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle722">你的伤不会影响你作战吧？</p>
<p begin="49669720000t" end="49700170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle723">不会，我只是失去一只眼睛</p>
<p begin="49701840000t" end="49733530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle724">神明给了我一只备用眼睛</p>
<p begin="49752300000t" end="49771910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle725">我的队长呢？</p>
<p begin="49784840000t" end="49822790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle726">他在咒骂神明，独自哀悼</p>
<p begin="49842390000t" end="49862000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle727">雷奥尼达！</p>
<p begin="49874090000t" end="49904120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle728">我们完了，我们死定了</p>
<p begin="49905790000t" end="49920390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle729">戴索斯，冷静点</p>
<p begin="49922060000t" end="49957920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle730">驼背叛徒带领敌军从后方突袭</p>
<p begin="49962100000t" end="49990460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle731">你派驻的福西昂人落荒而逃</p>
<p begin="49992130000t" end="50044260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle732">-这场战争结束了<br />-要等到我说结束才结束！</p>
<p begin="50045930000t" end="50089720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle733">我们会被幽灵战士团团包围<br />温泉关也会沦陷</p>
<p begin="50095980000t" end="50139770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle734">斯巴达壮士，准备光荣奋战到底</p>
<p begin="50141440000t" end="50173560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle735">光荣？你疯了吗？</p>
<p begin="50175230000t" end="50190660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle736">哪来的光荣奋战？</p>
<p begin="50196910000t" end="50232780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle737">只能选择撤退、投降或是死亡</p>
<p begin="50234450000t" end="50266150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle738">对我们来说选择很简单<br />阿卡迪人</p>
<p begin="50267820000t" end="50322870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle739">斯巴达壮士绝不退缩！<br />斯巴达壮士绝不投降！</p>
<p begin="50329130000t" end="50349980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle740">把这些话传出去</p>
<p begin="50352490000t" end="50389190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle741">让每个希腊人都知道真相</p>
<p begin="50390860000t" end="50419220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle742">让他们寻找自己的良知</p>
<p begin="50435900000t" end="50477610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle743">既然你在这里，也好好想想吧！</p>
<p begin="50552690000t" end="50575210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle744">我的手下要跟我离开</p>
<p begin="50628590000t" end="50651120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle745">愿神祝福你，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="50714100000t" end="50729950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle746">弟兄们！</p>
<p begin="50739540000t" end="50752890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle747">弟兄们！</p>
<p begin="50763310000t" end="50783330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle748">大伙儿集合</p>
<p begin="50802100000t" end="50834630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle749">绝不退缩、绝不投降</p>
<p begin="50836300000t" end="50875090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle750">这是斯巴达的律法</p>
<p begin="50877590000t" end="50928060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle751">根据斯巴达律法<br />我们要为斯巴达奋战到底</p>
<p begin="50929730000t" end="50949750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle752">死不足惜</p>
<p begin="50984370000t" end="51019400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle753">一个全新的时代来临了</p>
<p begin="51036500000t" end="51068200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle754">一个自由的时代</p>
<p begin="51078630000t" end="51115330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle755">世人将知道300名斯巴达壮士</p>
<p begin="51117000000t" end="51149950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle756">扞卫自由、誓死奋战</p>
<p begin="51352650000t" end="51370170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle757">我的朋友</p>
<p begin="51405620000t" end="51461510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle758">我这一生直到现在才有遗憾</p>
<p begin="51495290000t" end="51554520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle759">不是我儿子为国捐躯而感到遗憾</p>
<p begin="51573710000t" end="51612080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle760">而是我从来没跟他说我最爱他</p>
<p begin="51628340000t" end="51657120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle761">还有他光荣地与我并肩作战</p>
<p begin="51671300000t" end="51700500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle762">他遗传了我最好的部分</p>
<p begin="51791840000t" end="51817280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle763">我为你痛失爱子而心碎</p>
<p begin="51824370000t" end="51841470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle764">心？</p>
<p begin="51892360000t" end="51923220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle765">我的心…</p>
<p begin="51924890000t" end="51942410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle766">充满了仇恨</p>
<p begin="51983700000t" end="52000380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle767">很好</p>
<p begin="52091720000t" end="52110070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle768">狄里欧</p>
<p begin="52127180000t" end="52148450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle769">跟我来</p>
<p begin="52163040000t" end="52183900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle770">是的，吾王</p>
<p begin="52207670000t" end="52234370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle771">吾王，我仍可以上场作战</p>
<p begin="52236030000t" end="52267730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle772">没错，你是最优秀的战士之一</p>
<p begin="52270650000t" end="52306520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle773">但是你有其他人没有的能力</p>
<p begin="52333630000t" end="52367830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle774">你要用热情激昂的言语</p>
<p begin="52369500000t" end="52394530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle775">向议会传达我最后的命令</p>
<p begin="52419550000t" end="52442490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle776">告诉他们我们的故事</p>
<p begin="52444160000t" end="52489620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle777">让每位希腊人都知道300壮士<br />在这里的情形</p>
<p begin="52497960000t" end="52524240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle778">你要说一个伟大的故事</p>
<p begin="52542170000t" end="52553850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle779">一个胜利的故事</p>
<p begin="52565950000t" end="52581380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle780">胜利</p>
<p begin="52621840000t" end="52641860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle781">是的，吾王</p>
<p begin="52698580000t" end="52722350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle782">吾王，你有没有讯息…？</p>
<p begin="52751130000t" end="52764900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle783">要给王后的讯息？</p>
<p begin="52989290000t" end="53013480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle784">我什么也不用说</p>
<p begin="53164880000t" end="53188650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle785">数百名士兵离开战场</p>
<p begin="53195330000t" end="53219520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle786">少数人留下来</p>
<p begin="53271230000t" end="53297510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle787">只有一个人回头看</p>
<p begin="53400530000t" end="53422640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle788">斯巴达壮士！</p>
<p begin="53433480000t" end="53465180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle789">准备早餐，吃饱一点</p>
<p begin="53466850000t" end="53506050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle790">不过今晚<br />我们将在冥府大吃大喝</p>
<p begin="53594890000t" end="53621580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle791">容我让雷奥尼达的妻子</p>
<p begin="53623250000t" end="53667460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle792">斯巴达的王后发言</p>
<p begin="53784660000t" end="53803020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle793">-什么？<br />-不要紧的</p>
<p begin="53803850000t" end="53822200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle794">各位议员</p>
<p begin="53823870000t" end="53861410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle795">我不单以王后的身分站在这里</p>
<p begin="53870170000t" end="53897690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle796">也是以母亲的身分</p>
<p begin="53910210000t" end="53934400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle797">以妻子的身分</p>
<p begin="53952330000t" end="53977770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle798">以斯巴达女人的身分</p>
<p begin="54027820000t" end="54058690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle799">我以谦卑的态度站在这里</p>
<p begin="54092890000t" end="54117080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle800">我并非代表雷奥尼达发言</p>
<p begin="54117910000t" end="54147110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle801">他的行动比任何语言更强烈</p>
<p begin="54149610000t" end="54173800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle802">我代表没机会发言的那些人说话</p>
<p begin="54175470000t" end="54200910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle803">母亲、女儿、父亲、儿子</p>
<p begin="54202580000t" end="54232190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle804">300壮士为我们的权利而流血</p>
<p begin="54236370000t" end="54268480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle805">也为斯巴达的律法在奋战</p>
<p begin="54274740000t" end="54295590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle806">各位，这是一场战争</p>
<p begin="54299760000t" end="54325200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle807">我们必须派出斯巴达军队支援国王</p>
<p begin="54326460000t" end="54358150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle808">不是去救他，而是保护我们的后代</p>
<p begin="54363580000t" end="54394860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle809">请你们出兵扞卫自由</p>
<p begin="54396530000t" end="54419880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle810">伸张正义</p>
<p begin="54421550000t" end="54438650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle811">维护法律和秩序</p>
<p begin="54443240000t" end="54465340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle812">并且支持理性</p>
<p begin="54467010000t" end="54508300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle813">最重要的，是为了希望而出兵</p>
<p begin="54509970000t" end="54546260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle814">希望300壮士<br />不会在历史中白白牺牲</p>
<p begin="54553770000t" end="54588380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle815">他们的勇气让我们团结一心</p>
<p begin="54591300000t" end="54623420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle816">他们的义举让我们更坚强</p>
<p begin="54633430000t" end="54674300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle817">你们的决定则支持他们的勇气</p>
<p begin="54693490000t" end="54705170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle818">300</p>
<p begin="54733530000t" end="54751880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle819">我们必须出兵支援</p>
<p begin="54789840000t" end="54808190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle820">你说得很感人</p>
<p begin="54811520000t" end="54840300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle821">很有力、很有热忱</p>
<p begin="54844470000t" end="54887020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle822">可惜这场战争是你丈夫自找的</p>
<p begin="54887850000t" end="54912040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle823">你错了<br />这是瑟西斯发动的战争</p>
<p begin="54913710000t" end="54938730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle824">之前他父亲大流士<br />则是发动了马拉松之战</p>
<p begin="54940400000t" end="54957500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle825">波斯人绝对不会罢手</p>
<p begin="54959170000t" end="54992950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle826">直到我们的国家被夷为平地</p>
<p begin="54997130000t" end="55034250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle827">议会不需要你给我们上历史课</p>
<p begin="55039250000t" end="55059270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle828">那你要我给你们上什么课？</p>
<p begin="55063020000t" end="55083880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle829">我要一一说出来吗？</p>
<p begin="55088050000t" end="55122250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle830">尊严、责任、荣耀</p>
<p begin="55125170000t" end="55175640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle831">你说尊严、责任和荣耀？</p>
<p begin="55188570000t" end="55200660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle832">何不说说通奸？</p>
<p begin="55202330000t" end="55227360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle833">-好大的胆子<br />-我好大的胆子？</p>
<p begin="55231530000t" end="55261560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle834">大家仔细看看她</p>
<p begin="55263220000t" end="55297840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle835">她是个满嘴谎言的荡妇</p>
<p begin="55298680000t" end="55326200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle836">别想在这座圣殿说谎，王后</p>
<p begin="55327870000t" end="55359150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle837">数小时前你勾引我</p>
<p begin="55360820000t" end="55405030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle838">我若意志不坚，就会中你的圈套</p>
<p begin="55406700000t" end="55436730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle839">-你太过分了<br />-喔，伪君子说话了</p>
<p begin="55438400000t" end="55468430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle840">难道她没有给你吃甜头？</p>
<p begin="55470100000t" end="55502630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle841">请你安排让她在议会发言吗？</p>
<p begin="55504300000t" end="55521820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle842">-这是谎言<br />-是吗？</p>
<p begin="55523480000t" end="55561020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle843">你没有邀请他到国王寝室</p>
<p begin="55566440000t" end="55612740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle844">就像你请我到那里试图勾引我一样？</p>
<p begin="55639430000t" end="55674050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle845">你们的表情很惊讶<br />她用肉体当贿赂</p>
<p begin="55675720000t" end="55708670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle846">她的丈夫则发动战争引起混乱</p>
<p begin="55737870000t" end="55749960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle847">他说的是事实</p>
<p begin="55756220000t" end="55787920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle848">你就算辩才无碍也无话可说了</p>
<p begin="55789580000t" end="55811270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle849">你这个淫荡的王后</p>
<p begin="55857990000t" end="55876340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle850">你算是什么王后？</p>
<p begin="55893020000t" end="55926800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle851">赶快把她带下去，以免她再玷污</p>
<p begin="55927640000t" end="55956420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle852">公正的议会</p>
<p begin="56024400000t" end="56040250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle853">这不会很快结束</p>
<p begin="56053600000t" end="56089050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle854">你也不会喜欢<br />因为我不是你的王后</p>
<p begin="56310520000t" end="56330120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle855">他是叛徒</p>
<p begin="56335130000t" end="56383510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle856">叛徒…叛徒…</p>
<p begin="56387260000t" end="56408540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle857">叛徒…</p>
<p begin="56778910000t" end="56838970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle858">雷奥尼达，我不得不佩服你</p>
<p begin="56840630000t" end="56877340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle859">你把一场灾难转换成胜利</p>
<p begin="56879010000t" end="56909040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle860">虽然你狂妄自大</p>
<p begin="56910700000t" end="56952410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle861">吾王很欣赏你们的勇气和战技</p>
<p begin="56959920000t" end="56973680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle862">你会是强大的盟友</p>
<p begin="56975350000t" end="56987450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle863">投降吧，雷奥尼达</p>
<p begin="57004130000t" end="57032910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle864">用你的理智为你的手下着想</p>
<p begin="57061270000t" end="57077540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle865">我求求你</p>
<p begin="57083380000t" end="57102980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle866">听你希腊同胞的话</p>
<p begin="57104650000t" end="57141770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle867">他可以证明神王有多慈悲</p>
<p begin="57143440000t" end="57188060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle868">虽然你羞辱他、亵渎他</p>
<p begin="57197240000t" end="57229360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle869">万王之王仍然愿意原谅你</p>
<p begin="57231440000t" end="57261890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle870">只要你效忠于他<br />就会得到奖赏</p>
<p begin="57264390000t" end="57277740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle871">你为了你的土地而战？</p>
<p begin="57284830000t" end="57303180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle872">土地还是归你</p>
<p begin="57310270000t" end="57329870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle873">你为了斯巴达而战？</p>
<p begin="57331540000t" end="57371580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle874">斯巴达将比以前更富强</p>
<p begin="57373670000t" end="57392850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle875">你为了你的王位而战？</p>
<p begin="57402030000t" end="57431640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle876">你将被封为全希腊之王</p>
<p begin="57433310000t" end="57476270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle877">只臣服于唯一的宇宙之主</p>
<p begin="57480020000t" end="57527570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle878">雷奥尼达，你将获得胜利</p>
<p begin="57529240000t" end="57555100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle879">只要你放下武器</p>
<p begin="57556770000t" end="57588460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle880">向瑟西斯王跪拜</p>
<p begin="57893350000t" end="57942990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle881">他在寒冬中面对野狼的30年后</p>
<p begin="57944650000t" end="57990120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle882">现在和过去一样<br />他的内心并不害怕</p>
<p begin="57991780000t" end="58043500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle883">只是蠢蠢欲动<br />他的感官比以前更敏锐</p>
<p begin="58051430000t" end="58099390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle884">冰凉的海风吹拂他身上的汗水</p>
<p begin="58101060000t" end="58116070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle885">海鸥在哀号</p>
<p begin="58117740000t" end="58160290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle886">一边大啖数千具浮尸一边抱怨</p>
<p begin="58176130000t" end="58227020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle887">他身后的300壮士沉着冷静</p>
<p begin="58234530000t" end="58269140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle888">每一位都愿意立刻为他而死</p>
<p begin="58295420000t" end="58308770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle889">每一位</p>
<p begin="58323780000t" end="58342970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle890">都准备迎接死亡</p>
<p begin="58498120000t" end="58527320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle891">他的头盔让他窒息</p>
<p begin="58734190000t" end="58762550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle892">他的盾牌沉重无比</p>
<p begin="58837630000t" end="58853060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle893">你的长矛</p>
<p begin="58940650000t" end="58954830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle894">你…</p>
<p begin="58959420000t" end="58979440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle895">厄菲阿尔特</p>
<p begin="59030320000t" end="59048670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle896">愿你长命百岁</p>
<p begin="59127080000t" end="59150020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle897">雷奥尼达，你的长矛</p>
<p begin="59822360000t" end="59838630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle898">史特里欧！</p>
<p begin="59938730000t" end="59954580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle899">把他们都给宰了！</p>
<p begin="59988360000t" end="60004210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle900">他的头盔让他窒息</p>
<p begin="60005880000t" end="60037160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle901">模糊他的视线，他必须看得很远</p>
<p begin="60050510000t" end="60088880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle902">他的盾牌太重，会让他瞄不准</p>
<p begin="60090550000t" end="60127250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle903">因为他的目标在远方</p>
<p begin="60772900000t" end="60818770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle904">传说我们斯巴达人<br />是海克力斯的后裔</p>
<p begin="60833370000t" end="60876750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle905">英勇的雷奥尼达是最好的证明</p>
<p begin="60878420000t" end="60919710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle906">他的怒吼又长又响亮</p>
<p begin="61220840000t" end="61236690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle907">吾王</p>
<p begin="61359310000t" end="61395600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle908">能死在你身边是我的荣幸</p>
<p begin="61411450000t" end="61456500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle909">能和你同生共死是我的荣幸</p>
<p begin="61665450000t" end="61686730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle910">我的王后</p>
<p begin="61768890000t" end="61786410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle911">我的妻子</p>
<p begin="61900690000t" end="61919040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle912">我的挚爱</p>
<p begin="63383000000t" end="63404270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle913">“记得我们”</p>
<p begin="63420960000t" end="63455580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle914">这是国王下的简单命令</p>
<p begin="63471010000t" end="63503120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle915">“记得我们为什么牺牲”</p>
<p begin="63523140000t" end="63563600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle916">他并不希望后人用诗歌</p>
<p begin="63581950000t" end="63624080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle917">或纪念碑<br />来记载这场战争和他的英勇事蹟</p>
<p begin="63652440000t" end="63675800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle918">他的命令很简单</p>
<p begin="63729180000t" end="63750040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle919">他跟我说：</p>
<p begin="63760460000t" end="63777560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle920">“记得我们”</p>
<p begin="63794250000t" end="63816350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle921">这是他的心愿</p>
<p begin="63818440000t" end="63855980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle922">如果有人在千百年以后…</p>
<p begin="63863480000t" end="63896850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle923">经过这场惨烈战役发生的地点</p>
<p begin="63901020000t" end="63926880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle924">希望我们的声音</p>
<p begin="63928550000t" end="63969420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle925">能在他们的耳边低吟</p>
<p begin="63979020000t" end="64015300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle926">请你们告诉斯巴达人</p>
<p begin="64018640000t" end="64077450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle927">我们在这里扞卫斯巴达的尊严</p>
<p begin="64104970000t" end="64132080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle928">我的国王光荣地死去</p>
<p begin="64140840000t" end="64167120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle929">我的同袍弟兄也壮烈牺牲</p>
<p begin="64190890000t" end="64215500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle930">那只是一年前的事</p>
<p begin="64254710000t" end="64307260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle931">我一直在思索他提到的胜利</p>
<p begin="64309760000t" end="64336040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle932">时间证明他是对的</p>
<p begin="64344800000t" end="64375240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle933">那场惨烈的战争和英勇的事蹟</p>
<p begin="64376910000t" end="64423210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle934">传到希腊每个角落<br />雷奥尼达和300壮士</p>
<p begin="64424880000t" end="64444900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle935">远离家园</p>
<p begin="64446570000t" end="64480350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle936">不只是为了斯巴达而壮烈牺牲</p>
<p begin="64482020000t" end="64519970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle937">也是为了全希腊人民<br />以及这个国家未来的荣耀</p>
<p begin="64529150000t" end="64580030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle938">现在，在被称为普拉蒂亚的土地上</p>
<p begin="64581700000t" end="64628410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle939">瑟西斯率领的大军将面临灭亡</p>
<p begin="64648430000t" end="64682220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle940">幽灵战士聚集在对面</p>
<p begin="64683890000t" end="64732680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle941">他们的内心充满了恐惧</p>
<p begin="64734350000t" end="64753540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle942">他们冰冷的手指紧握胸口</p>
<p begin="64755210000t" end="64787320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle943">因为他们清楚记得</p>
<p begin="64788990000t" end="64814430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle944">300壮士的长矛和利刃有多可怕</p>
<p begin="64828610000t" end="64884090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle945">他们看着对面的一万名斯巴达士兵</p>
<p begin="64885750000t" end="64918700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle946">率领着三万名自由的希腊人</p>
<p begin="64987110000t" end="65025890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle947">敌军的人数只比我们多了三倍</p>
<p begin="65028810000t" end="65048830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle948">不过希腊人拥有很大的胜算</p>
<p begin="65055920000t" end="65103050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle949">今天，我们将消灭邪恶和暴政</p>
<p begin="65104720000t" end="65144760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle950">带来我们想像不到的光明未来</p>
<p begin="65192730000t" end="65207740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle951">弟兄们，衷心感谢</p>
<p begin="65214830000t" end="65252370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle952">雷奥尼达和英勇的300壮士</p>
<p begin="65254040000t" end="65281570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle953">胜利在望！</p>
